# Streaming Configuration — Athens, April 2026
**E.I. Werner / Outside Inn Studios**
*Reference document for AI project context and Athens Tech Stack updates. Verified against OBS logs and live test streams on April 18, 2026.*

---

## Purpose of This Document

This is the authoritative record of the streaming configuration used in Athens as of April 18, 2026, and — more importantly — **why it is configured this way**. The configuration is the result of a multi-week diagnostic process that isolated the root cause of persistent dropped-frame problems across multiple streams (MM09, MM10, and others). Previous configurations failed because of a specific, non-obvious OBS behavior under RTMPS. The current configuration avoids that behavior.

If any AI assistant is asked to modify streaming settings in the future, this document must be read first. Settings are interdependent. Changing one without understanding why it is set that way can reintroduce the original problem.

---

